## TeachersLounge — Local Dev Environment Variables
## Copy this file to .env.local and fill in real values.
## .env.local is gitignored and must never be committed.
##
## Services start with placeholder defaults if variables are unset,
## but AI features require real API keys to function.

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=localdevpassword

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_PASSWORD=localredispassword

# ── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
JWT_SECRET=replace-with-32-byte-random-hex

# ── AI Providers (required for tutoring to work) ──────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ── LiteLLM ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Master key that services use to call the ai-gateway
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 16
LITELLM_MASTER_KEY=localdevmasterkey

# ── Stripe (optional for Phase 1 local dev) ───────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
